These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
2 different games are played: whist, chess
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, davidoff
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Hobby   | board-games    | filmmaking |
| Game         | chess | whist    |
| Cigar     | bolivar     | davidoff      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy
2 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Flower      | daisy  | amaryllis   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | turtle  |
| Birthday     | december   | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, dutch
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, orange
House: tower, gothic-revival
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Nationality         | chinese   | dutch  |
| Color   | orange | azure  |
| House         | tower   | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
