There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| House          | craftsman | colonial |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | milk   |
| Sport     | skateboarding       | ice-hockey      |

