.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving
There are 2 different nationalities: german, pakistani
House: palace, colonial
1. the colonial house is on the left of the german##1
2. the palace house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Hobby    | skydiving | fishing     |
| Nationality     | pakistani | german |
| House   | colonial | palace    |

